{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Capital_s_Underworld_The_Constituents",
  "title": "The Constituents",
  "summary": "Senator Tokoga slips away to Organa Park for a quiet meeting with Ord Mantell's Senator Ivanil Sandomere, who fears the pair were set up amid the corruption scandal engulfing their offices. The medic Myiari and the news-obsessed Johanna join them before Sandomere departs, but the conversation is interrupted when two cloaked, armored Quarren emerge from the woods and trap Tokoga and Myiari, accusing the senator of betraying his people by embezzling funds into a secret account in his cousin's name. Tokoga insists the funds were a charitable trust for victims of the Civil War and that he is being framed by Nass, while Myiari nearly draws her blaster in his defense. A lost Sluissi pilot, Shane, stumbles into the standoff and tries to defuse it, claiming Republic authority and suggesting the hot-headed Quarren may himself be Nass's plant. In the end the Quarren leader gives Tokoga one week to prove his innocence before they vanish back into the woods, leaving the threat of death hanging over him.",
